// Vendored stand-in for the generated Builtins.pkl from the hk@1.48.0 pkl
// package. Rebuilt from the hk 1.48.0 crate sources (crates.io) because the
// GitHub release zip is unreachable from sandboxed CI/agent environments.
// Update by re-vendoring pkl/ when bumping the hk version in mise.toml.
// The deprecated check/fix_byte_order_marker aliases are intentionally not
// re-exported (use byte_order_marker).
